						<summary>

						<p>This is much damaged, and seems to record a transaction by the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Aparājita-chaturvēdimaṅgalam</hi> in Perundarappuram situated in Purisai-nāḍu (about some land). Mention is made of <hi rend="italic">sabhai-vāriyam, ēri-vāriyam</hi> and other committees of the assembly. This might be a record of <hi rend="bold">Uttama-Chōḷa.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
